# CheckIdAttribute

## OutOfRangeId

<!-- Description, Properties, ... sections are auto-generated. -->
<!-- REPLACE ME AUTO-GENERATION -->

### Details

A ParameterGroup should have a unique id > 0 and <= 10000.
Note that from DM 9.0.4 onward, id > 0 and <=100.000 can be used.
